{"title_page": "Invoicera", "text_new": "{{Orphan|date=June 2016}}\n\n{{Infobox software\n| name                   = Invoicera \n| logo                   = Invoicera.jpg\n| logo caption           = Invoicera logo\n| genre                  = [[Software as a service]]\n| website                = {{URL|invoicera.com}}\n}}\n'''Invoicera''' is an online invoicing software.<ref name=\"Cozma2012-08-17\">{{cite news |last=Cozma |first=Nicole |date=2012-08-17 |title=Use Invoicera for free small business invoicing services |url=http://www.cnet.com/how-to/use-invoicera-for-free-small-business-invoicing-services/ |publisher=[[CNET]] |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6a56zjOhj?url=http://www.cnet.com/how-to/use-invoicera-for-free-small-business-invoicing-services/ |archivedate=2015-07-17 }}</ref>\n\nIt allows users to monitor, dispatch, and accept invoices in one [[web service]]. After signing up for the service, users are assigned a personal subdomain to set up their invoice configuration. It allows users to add clients' data to the service through uploading a [[Microsoft Excel]] file.<ref name=\"Weisbein2012-02-14\">{{cite news |last=Weisbein |first=Jeff |date=2012-02-14 |title=Invoicera Review: Making Invoicing Simple |url=http://www.besttechie.com/2012/02/14/invoicera-review/ |newspaper=BestTechie |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6a574OgyS?url=http://www.besttechie.com/2012/02/14/invoicera-review/ |archivedate=2015-07-17 }}</ref>\n\nInvoicera is compatible with businesses of varying sizes, including [[freelancer]]s, [[small business]]es, and large businesses.<ref name=\"Hendricks2015-05-26\">{{cite news |last=Hendricks |first=Drew |date=2015-05-26 |title=10 Online Invoicing Services for Small-Business Owners |url=http://www.entrepreneur.com/article/246197 |newspaper=[[Entrepreneur (magazine)|Entrepreneur]] |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6a59RoPWc?url=http://www.entrepreneur.com/article/246197 |archivedate=2015-07-17 }}</ref> It is compatible with [[Basecamp (company)|Basecamp]], a [[project management|project-management]] tool, so Invoicera can upload data from Basecamp.<ref name=\"Long2015-07-10\">{{cite news |last=Long |first=Jonathan |date=2015-07-10 |title=5 Online Invoicing Solutions for Business Owners |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jonathan-long/5-online-invoicing-soluti_b_7765718.html |newspaper=[[The Huffington Post]] |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6a59PU0A3?url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jonathan-long/5-online-invoicing-soluti_b_7765718.html |archivedate=2015-07-17 }}</ref> The software interfaces with more than 25 [[payment gateway]]s.<ref name=\"Turner2019-01-23\">{{cite news |last=Turner |first=Brian |date=2019-01-23 |title=Best billing and invoicing software of 2019 |url=https://www.techradar.com/best/best-billing-and-invoicing-software |publisher=[[TechRadar]] |accessdate=2019-04-01 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/77IrIGGSj?url=https://www.techradar.com/best/best-billing-and-invoicing-software |archivedate=2019-04-01 }}</ref> It supports [[subscription]]s and repeated [[invoice]]s and allows clients to schedule [[late fee]]s when payments have not been made on time.<ref name=\"Turner2019-01-23\"/> Invoicera uses [[freemium]] model, letting users dispatch an unrestricted number of invoices to at most three customers.<ref name=\"Long2015-07-10\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|invoicera.com}}\n\n[[Category:Web applications]]\n", "text_old": "{{Orphan|date=June 2016}}\n\n{{Infobox software\n| name                   = Invoicera \n| logo                   = Invoicera.jpg\n| logo caption           = Invoicera logo\n| genre                  = [[Software as a service]]\n| website                = {{URL|invoicera.com}}\n}}\n'''Invoicera''' is an online invoicing software.<ref name=\"Cozma2012-08-17\">{{cite news |last=Cozma |first=Nicole |date=2012-08-17 |title=Use Invoicera for free small business invoicing services |url=http://www.cnet.com/how-to/use-invoicera-for-free-small-business-invoicing-services/ |publisher=[[CNET]] |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6a56zjOhj?url=http://www.cnet.com/how-to/use-invoicera-for-free-small-business-invoicing-services/ |archivedate=2015-07-17 }}</ref>\n\nIt allows users to monitor, dispatch, and accept invoices in one [[web service]]. After signing up for the service, users are assigned a personal subdomain to set up their invoice configuration. It allows users to add clients' data to the service through uploading a [[Microsoft Excel]] file.<ref name=\"Weisbein2012-02-14\">{{cite news |last=Weisbein |first=Jeff |date=2012-02-14 |title=Invoicera Review: Making Invoicing Simple |url=http://www.besttechie.com/2012/02/14/invoicera-review/ |newspaper=BestTechie |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6a574OgyS?url=http://www.besttechie.com/2012/02/14/invoicera-review/ |archivedate=2015-07-17 }}</ref>\n\nInvoicera is compatible with businesses of varying sizes, including [[freelancer]]s, [[small business]]es, and large businesses.<ref name=\"Hendricks2015-05-26\">{{cite news |last=Hendricks |first=Drew |date=2015-05-26 |title=10 Online Invoicing Services for Small-Business Owners |url=http://www.entrepreneur.com/article/246197 |newspaper=[[Entrepreneur (magazine)|Entrepreneur]] |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6a59RoPWc?url=http://www.entrepreneur.com/article/246197 |archivedate=2015-07-17 }}</ref> It is compatible with [[Basecamp (company)|Basecamp]], a [[project management|project-management]] tool, so Invoicera can upload data from Basecamp.<ref name=\"Long2015-07-10\">{{cite news |last=Long |first=Jonathan |date=2015-07-10 |title=5 Online Invoicing Solutions for Business Owners |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jonathan-long/5-online-invoicing-soluti_b_7765718.html |newspaper=[[The Huffington Post]] |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6a59PU0A3?url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jonathan-long/5-online-invoicing-soluti_b_7765718.html |archivedate=2015-07-17 }}</ref> The software interfaces with more than 25 [[payment gateway]]s.<ref name=\"Turner2019-01-23\">{{cite news |last=Turner |first=Brian |date=2019-01-23 |title=Best billing and invoicing software of 2019 |url=https://www.techradar.com/best/best-billing-and-invoicing-software |publisher=[[TechRadar]] |accessdate=2019-04-01 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/77IrIGGSj?url=https://www.techradar.com/best/best-billing-and-invoicing-software |archivedate=2019-04-01 }}</ref> It supports [[subscription]]s and repeated [[invoice]]s and allows clients to schedule [[late fee]]s when payments have not been made on time.<ref name=\"Turner2019-01-23\"/> Invoicera uses [[freemium]] model, letting users dispatch an unrestricted number of invoices to at most three customers.<ref name=\"Long2015-07-10\"/>\n\nWriting in the magazine ''[[Entrepreneur (magazine)|Entrepreneur]]'', Andrew Cravenho praised Invoicera's task management tool, which allows users to record how much time each project took. Calling it Invoicera's \"most striking feature\", Cravenho said that although \"the idea of a time-tracking tool is nothing new, what Invoicera does differently is allow you to assign and evaluate tasks in order to enhance productivity\".<ref name=\"Cravenho2015-05-07\">{{cite news |last=Cravenho |first=Andrew |date=2015-05-07 |title=5 Invoicing and Accounting Tools for New Entrepreneurs |url=http://www.entrepreneur.com/article/245775 |newspaper=[[Entrepreneur (magazine)|Entrepreneur]] |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6a59X1VAj?url=http://www.entrepreneur.com/article/245775 |archivedate=2015-07-17 }}</ref> Brian Turner wrote in [[TechRadar]] that Invoicera had fewer templates compared to the other services he reviewed but \"the ones offered are fully customizable\".<ref name=\"Turner2019-01-23\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|invoicera.com}}\n\n[[Category:Web applications]]\n", "name_user": "TeddyCruz", "label": "safe", "comment": "Removed Spam", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Invoicera"}
